        <h2 id="core-skills">Core skills</h2>
        <p>You may have come to content design from a variety of backgrounds – such as communications, marketing, web editing, copywriting, technical writing, journalism.</p>

        <h3>Plain language</h3>
        <p>Content designers need to know the basics of <a href="#">good readability</a>. They’re aware how readers scan content. There’s a skill involved in improving content for ease of use. They will know how to create signposts for users, mix up the length of sentences and use active language. They work hard to make the meaning succinct and clear.</p>
